   <i> ♪ Woke up this morning</i>
   <i> feeling tired and small ♪</i>

135
00:07:17,604 --> 00:07:21,573
    <i> ♪ But look at us now! We</i>
  <i> must be ninety feet tall. ♪</i>

136
00:07:21,775 --> 00:07:24,676
     <i> ♪ Don't have to worry</i>
    <i> 'bout making mistakes ♪</i>

137
00:07:24,778 --> 00:07:28,981
      <i> ♪ because being big</i>
       <i> is all it takes! ♪</i>

