00:07:29,583 --> 00:07:32,617
  <i> ♪ A tiny twist of fate</i>
 <i> brought on this big change. ♪</i>

139
00:07:32,719 --> 00:07:34,686
 <i> ♪ Give me room, gotta zoom! ♪</i>

140
00:07:34,788 --> 00:07:36,788
 <i> ♪ I've got plans to arrange ♪</i>

141
00:07:36,890 --> 00:07:40,659
 <i> ♪ Can do what I want, be</i>
  <i> it run, trot, or traipse, ♪</i>

142
00:07:40,761 --> 00:07:44,163
       <i> ♪ 'cause being big</i>
       <i> is all it takes. ♪</i>

