   <i> ♪ At bedtime we don't even</i>
   <i> have to close our eyes. ♪</i>

145
00:07:52,005 --> 00:07:56,041
    <i> ♪ We're in control now,</i>
      <i> for goodness sake ♪</i>

146
00:07:56,243 --> 00:07:59,945
       <i> ♪ 'cause being big</i>
       <i> is all it takes! ♪</i>

147
00:08:00,547 --> 00:08:03,582
   <i> ♪ Leaving behind the</i>
  <i> little pony you've known, ♪</i>

148
00:08:03,684 --> 00:08:07,719
  <i> ♪ steppin' out, growin' up,</i>
   <i> makin' moves of my own. ♪</i>

149
00:08:07,921 --> 00:08:09,488
   <i> ♪ You can't tell me no. ♪</i>

150
00:08:09,590 --> 00:08:11,790
<i>♪ There's no place I can't go: ♪</i>

151
00:08:11,992 --> 00:08:15,594
      <i> ♪ mountains, cities,</i>
      <i> jungles, or lakes, ♪</i>

152
00:08:15,696 --> 00:08:19,097
       <i> ♪ 'cause being big</i>
       <i> is all it takes. ♪</i>

153
